    "name": "团地日和",
    "steam_appid": 3107530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让夏日祭再次伟大！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传统的夏日祭典，随着时代变迁与老龄化逐渐凋零。但居住在这里的少女星乃，却准备为了她的朋友们，以及罹患认知障碍症的奶奶，重新举办一届远比过往更加盛大的夏日祭！漫步在日式街坊中，与各种奇妙有趣的邻居们成为朋友，通关多种小游戏获取秘密，并在温馨与阴暗并存的网络世界中游历。让我们与星乃、她的朋友们，以及患有认知障碍的奶奶，一起走过这段笑中带泪的大冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是……什么是「团地」？这是日本的大型住宅区，或者你可以把它想象成曾经无比常见的“铁西小区”。这里曾经人声鼎沸，但也不总是欢声笑语：如今的团地折射出诸多社会问题——从老龄化、认知障碍症到孤独感等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星乃将如何用她纯真的童心与好奇心面对这些挑战？让我们一探究竟！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/2326786515bb10556e9af06e7bc514fa.poster.avif?t=1766748864\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/2326786515bb10556e9af06e7bc514fa.webm?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/2326786515bb10556e9af06e7bc514fa.mp4?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性鲜明的左邻右里</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因各种原因，逐渐忘却了夏日祭的居民……或许可以通过完成一些小挑战，来改变他们的想法？有人在被烈日晒得滚烫的滑梯上煎荷包蛋，也有人蹲在水坑边专注地Cos寿司主理人，还有完全沉浸在扫地僧角色中的竹爷爷……该如何让他们回忆起曾经夏日祭的欢笑与烟火呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/4f8ff3ef3c58ecb8479caab78a7be14b.poster.avif?t=1766748864\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/4f8ff3ef3c58ecb8479caab78a7be14b.webm?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/4f8ff3ef3c58ecb8479caab78a7be14b.mp4?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用网络收集情报</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好在时代的发展不总是带来疏远，使用爸爸开发的小型社交软件「邻里在线」，可以访问大家的个人主页，或者靠关键词在网上搜索想要的情报。集合这些线索，目标只有一个：成功举办夏日祭！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/3e6f43744e318f883012a21fcef5f83e.poster.avif?t=1766748864\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/3e6f43744e318f883012a21fcef5f83e.webm?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/3e6f43744e318f883012a21fcef5f83e.mp4?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >靠「感应游戏」探索团地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还记得奶奶说，只要发动五感认知世界，就会发现更多的惊喜与奇遇！比如细细品味青草与树木的芬芳，凝神注视杯沿上的露珠，侧耳倾听自来水在管道中的流动声……然后化身五角星！摆出星星的姿态就能对感应游戏发起挑战，快来试试吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/ff6266a281c423896601b343a6d9a7ff.poster.avif?t=1766748864\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/ff6266a281c423896601b343a6d9a7ff.webm?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/ff6266a281c423896601b343a6d9a7ff.mp4?t=1766748864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >来认识下主角们吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/db1be2f6387a6d9462e935e3015988a2.avif?t=1766748864\" width=304 height=278 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲金冈 星乃</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过于活泼的六年级学生！因父亲工作缘故，她曾随家人在美国生活五年，最近刚与父亲一起回到故乡「某座团地」，和奶奶共同生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/487d971963029244e33e152860e37efc.avif?t=1766748864\" width=304 height=278 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲金冈 公子（星乃的奶奶）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前任幼儿园园长，星乃最敬爱的奶奶！虽已罹患失智症数年，但在她健康时，曾教导星乃和理央各种知识与技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/00cb4d9508b7cd550ee95002e36eb0fc.avif?t=1766748864\" width=304 height=278 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲一色 理央</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在团地土生土长的少年，与星乃曾是亲密的童年玩伴。但自从星乃搬回团地后，他对星乃和奶奶的态度却变得疏离起来……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107530/extras/c745984613fbd30b0965ac9150a3d3f7.avif?t=1766748864\" width=304 height=187 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲胡瓜郎</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘的胡瓜郎！某天突然现身帮助星乃筹备夏日祭典，但似乎对自己的过往记忆模糊不清。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发团队</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >sandy powder 负责日文剧本撰写并参与游戏共同设计；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Melos Han-Tani（代表作《镇痛 1+2》《恒远之海》《Sephonie》及《Angeline Era》）负责程序开发、音乐制作、游戏设计及英文翻译；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >mogumu 担任美术设计；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Olivia 与 ume 协助市场推广工作。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
